WEBVTT

00:04:58.030 --> 00:05:03.942
And we can match their courage
by not looking away or turning our backs,

00:05:03.966 --> 00:05:06.537
by helping those
who are helping themselves,

00:05:06.561 --> 00:05:08.997
and together, save more lives.

00:05:09.956 --> 00:05:11.107
Thank you.

00:05:11.131 --> 00:05:12.326
(Applause)

00:05:12.350 --> 00:05:13.510
(Cheers)

00:05:13.534 --> 00:05:17.940
(Applause)

00:05:17.964 --> 00:05:19.868
Shoham Arad: Come over here, please.

00:05:20.538 --> 00:05:22.379
Why are hospitals being bombed?

00:05:22.966 --> 00:05:24.568
Rola Hallam: Yeah, good question.

00:05:24.592 --> 00:05:27.578
So, Physicians for Human Rights
have documented

00:05:27.602 --> 00:05:29.237
nearly 500 attacks on hospitals

00:05:29.261 --> 00:05:32.013
and over 800 medical personnel
who have been killed --